---
layout: base
permalink: /coalition/apply/
title: "Apply to the Coalition — E5 Enclave | Liberty City Miami"
description: "Apply to join the E5 Enclave Coalition of the Willing — Black-led organizations, individual builders, funders, and partner institutions. Tell us what you build."
extraJs:
  - /assets/js/forms.js
breadcrumbs:
  - { label: "Coalition", url: "/coalition/" }
  - { label: "Apply" }
---
<header class="vc-page-head reveal">
  <div class="vc-page-eyebrow">Coalition · Application</div>
  <h1 class="vc-page-h">Apply to <em>the Coalition.</em></h1>
  <p class="vc-page-deck">Tell us who you are, what you steward, and how you would contribute. A member of the Council will respond personally — usually within five business days.</p>
</header>

<form class="vc-form reveal" data-vc-form data-subject="coalition-apply" data-endpoint="/api/contact" novalidate>
  <div class="field-row">
    <div class="row">
      <label for="apply-name">Name</label>
      <input id="apply-name" name="name" type="text" required autocomplete="name"/>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <label for="apply-org">Organization</label>
      <input id="apply-org" name="organization" type="text" autocomplete="organization"/>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="field-row">
    <div class="row">
      <label for="apply-email">Email</label>
      <input id="apply-email" name="email" type="email" required autocomplete="email"/>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <label for="apply-role">Role</label>
      <input id="apply-role" name="role" type="text" autocomplete="organization-title"/>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <label for="apply-track">Track</label>
    <select id="apply-track" name="track" required>
      <option value="">Select…</option>
      <option value="institutional">Institutional member (Black-led organization)</option>
      <option value="individual">Individual builder</option>
      <option value="partner">Partner institution / aligned coalition</option>
      <option value="funder">Funder / institutional partner</option>
    </select>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <label for="apply-pillar">Primary pillar interest</label>
    <select id="apply-pillar" name="pillar">
      <option value="">No preference / multiple</option>
      <option value="environmental">Environmental — Lineage Farms · FarmBlock</option>
      <option value="economic">Economic</option>
      <option value="educational">Educational — McCartney Academy</option>
      <option value="engagement">Engagement — Block to the Boardroom</option>
      <option value="emancipated">Emancipated — Restitution 246</option>
    </select>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <label for="apply-msg">What would you contribute, and what do you hope to gain?</label>
    <textarea id="apply-msg" name="message" required></textarea>
  </div>
  <div class="actions">
    <button type="submit" class="vc-cta-primary" data-label="Submit application">Submit application <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></button>
    <span class="hint">Or email <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.primary }}" style="color:var(--vc-oxblood); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vc-rule-2);">{{ site.contact.primary }}</a></span>
  </div>
</form>

<div class="vc-form-success" role="status">
  <strong style="font-family: var(--vc-text); font-size: 9.5px; letter-spacing: 0.42em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--vc-oxblood); display: block; margin-bottom: 8px;">Received.</strong>
  Thank you. A member of the Council will respond personally — usually within five business days. The center holds.
</div>
